---
title: Beef Bulgogi with fragrant jasmine rice
description: Bulgogi is a Korean BBQ dish that can feature many proteins—but is most often cooked with beef. The richness of the meat pairs well with the tangy and smoky BBQ flavour bulgogi is known for.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R06_W18_IE_IEQCLB13531-3_Main_high-588fdc3b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/bbq-beef-bulgogi-63d8f2df85a76906e4f26b2b-c97d07b5.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipes/beef-bulgogi-63d8f2df85a76906e4f26b2b
author: HelloFresh
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: Asian
servings: 2
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 561 kcal
  fat: 5 g
  saturated fat: 2.3 g
  carbohydrates: 81.3 g
  sugar: 10.7 g
